Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关炎至急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魅于珠红
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之言语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血色梦终

Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开车小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们要去敦贺的一个叫神乐的小村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的同伴之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敦巴守护着那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是画酒船里那副画的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我这也是第一次去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经20年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了逃避战争隐居在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久远 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过黑蜜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 也没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说她在神乐很受人们崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来带黑蜜去那里是为了幽禁她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在村民们倒是自愿地想要保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际见过她的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有沙仁轮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这回也是头一次知道她的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得黑蜜她是个怎么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该比我们更清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对她一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总有这种莫名的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所知的就是黑蜜夫人的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜夫人非常想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外还需要别的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿开始我们得走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜真的会在这种深山老林里 沙仁轮？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了避敌人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而神乐是最佳场所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是脱离世俗的人们居住的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么了 歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“地鼠”啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受“浩劫”的影响 各地建造了很多地下村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿就是…神乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家去里面等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…好安静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连个人影都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁轮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有个活的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敦巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敦巴 到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 敦巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常春藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常春藤和人的血？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 他们被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是赤帝军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁轮 你知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说有个能操纵森林的藤蔓来杀人的魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜夫人说不定也被他们带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看还有没有人活着 我们分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敦巴 你留在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不累
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闻下就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不是铁打的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己保重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来这儿已经全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说不定敌人还躲在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库玛斯 连这么勇敢的你都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他很熟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库玛斯是弓箭的达人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他射出的箭仿佛能跟踪猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪的手能准确无误地找出人们的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有这种特异功能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是“浩劫”导致的变异
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,付出了一部分牺牲的同时 我们得到了超乎常人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到神乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里也已经有敌人在等着我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们迟早会找到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们在一起就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我轻松不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错觉吗 感觉身体很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像血在翻滚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是还没达到完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体的治愈能力跟不上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以根本用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍一下就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜她是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底看见什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁轮她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你们能活着出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这顽强的生命力还是要表扬下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好个愣小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不和你提个醒 你连自己要去天堂还是地狱都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你们
